<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">50-page rule! Until the age of fifty if you are not into a book by page 50, skip it. For every year after the age of fifty read one less page before y<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">50-page rule! Until the age of fifty if you are not into a book by page 50, skip it. For every year after the age of fifty read one less page before you make your decision. ie. A sixty-year-old person only has to read 40 pages. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
