<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer10749546229949330884">Chloe Benjamin is the author of THE IMMORTALISTS, a New York Times Bestseller, #1 Indie Next Pick for January 2018, Barnes &amp; Noble Discover Great New Writers Selection, #1 Library Reads pick, and Amazon Best Book of the Month.<br/><br/>Her first novel, THE ANATOMY OF DREAMS (Atria, 2014), received the Edna Ferber Fiction Book Award and was longlisted for the 2014 Flaherty-Dunnan First Novel Prize. <br/><br/>Her novel</span>
  <span id="freeText10749546229949330884" style="display:none">Chloe Benjamin is the author of THE IMMORTALISTS, a New York Times Bestseller, #1 Indie Next Pick for January 2018, Barnes &amp; Noble Discover Great New Writers Selection, #1 Library Reads pick, and Amazon Best Book of the Month.<br /><br />Her first novel, THE ANATOMY OF DREAMS (Atria, 2014), received the Edna Ferber Fiction Book Award and was longlisted for the 2014 Flaherty-Dunnan First Novel Prize. <br /><br />Her novels have been translated into over twenty-three languages. A graduate of Vassar College and the M.F.A. in fiction at the University of Wisconsin, Chloe lives with her husband in Madison, WI.</span>
  <a data-text-id="10749546229949330884" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

</div>
</div>

